Privacy Policy
Your privacy is important to us, and we take our responsibility of caring for it seriously. This policy describes what information Alda Games s.r.o. („Alda Games“, „we“, „our“, “us”) collects when you („user“) use the mobile, and downloadable games offered by Alda Games.
We encourage you to review our Privacy Policy carefully. By using our services, you agree to the terms outlined in the policy. If you don't agree with our practices, you can stop using our services at any time.
If you wish to delete your account in one of our games which support account creation, please,
check here
.
What information does the Application obtain?
Our primary objective in collecting user information is to provide and enhance the Service and to enable users to enjoy the Service.
When you install any of the Services, We may collect and record the information you provide to us, whether through the Services or through social network or other third party services (“Account Information”).
Personal information
“Personal information” means information about you that can be used to contact or identify you, including:
Your name or alias
Your social network and profile picture
Your mobile device’s unique identifier (UDID)
Transaction identifiers for purchases
Non-Personal information
We collect other information automatically when you use our products, including:
IP address
Information about the hardware you may own
Platform type
Game statistics (number of coins or XP)
Details about what our products you use and your use of them
Device event information, including crash reports, request and system activity details (e.g. whether you encountered an error playing our games or lost Internet access).
How We Use Your Information?
We use your personal and non-personal information, both individually and combined together, in the following ways:
Operate, improve, and develop our games and services
Populate online leaderboards and enable online matchmaking
Serve and measure the effectiveness of advertising and enable online matchmaking
Measure the health of our services
Provide game experiences that you may like
Identify, fix, and troubleshoot bugs and service errors
Save game progress and stats
Personalize advertising for you and deliver targeted marketing, service updates and promotional offers
Present offers and/or information relating to games you might like
Attribute installations to different source (Google Play, User Acquisition campaigns etc)
Children use and the application
We do not use the Application to knowingly solicit data from or market to children under the age of 13. If a parent or guardian becomes aware that his or her child has provided us with information without their consent, he or she should contact us. We will delete such information from our files within a reasonable time. We encourage you to participate in your child's web experience.
Information We Share with Third Parties
We use 3rd party services in our apps. These services collect usage data in compliance with their Privacy Policies. The services are described below.
Advertising
3rd party ad serving systems allow user data to be utilized for advertising communication purposes displayed in the form of banners and other advertisements on our apps, possibly based on user interests.
Ironsource
- We use Ironsource as the main ad server. Ironsource is reputable partner of all major advertising networks, including Google (AdMob), Unity and Meta (Facebook).
Analytics
3rd party analytics services allow us to monitor and analyze app usage, better understand our audience and user behavior.
Google Analytics -
Google Analytics is an analysis service provided by Google Inc. Google utilizes the collected data to track and examine the use of app, to prepare reports on user activities and share them with other Google services. Google may use the data to contextualize and personalize the ads of its own advertising network.
AppsFlyer -
AppsFlyer is standard MMP (mobile measurement partner). We use it to attribute installs from our User Acquisition campaigns and measure effectivity of these campaigns on campaign-level. AppsFlyer collects user data obtained from Google Play and also other sources - these data may include GEO (country or town) data and data of similar type and these data are used to analyze aspects of user acquisition campaings.
GameAnalytics -
GameAnalytics is popular analytics solution for games. We use it to gather data from the game itself on event-level to balance our games, fix bugs and make the game experience as pleasant as possible.
Changes to this privacy statement
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time for any reason. Use of information we collect now is subject to the Privacy Statement in effect at the time such information is used. If we make changes in the way we use personal information, we will notify you by posting an announcement on our site. Users are bound by any changes to the Privacy Statement when he or she uses or otherwise accesses the Application after such changes have been first posted.
Contact us
If you have any questions regarding privacy while using the Application, please contact us via email at info@aldagames.com.
Change log:
April 5, 2018 (created)
June 6, 2022 (updated with current information)
Cookie Policy
We use cookies, anonymous identifiers, and similar technologies to make our services better and more personalized for you. These tools also help us understand how our apps, games, and services are used so we can improve them.
How We Use Cookies and Similar Technologies
When you visit our website, use our apps, or interact with our content, we use technologies like cookies to collect information. This helps us:
Make your experience better: Remember your preferences (like language) and make things easier to use.
Keep things secure: Verify who you are and protect against fraud.
Understand what you like: See how you use our services so we can improve and offer you content you'll enjoy.
What are Cookies?
Cookies are tiny text files stored on your computer or phone. They help websites remember things about you. You can learn more about them at www.allaboutcookies.org.
Types of Technologies We Use
We use a few different types of technologies, some of which may collect personal data. These include:
Essential Cookies: These are necessary for you to log in and use our services.
Functionality Cookies: These let us remember your choices and personalize your experience.
Performance Cookies: These help us understand how people use our services so we can make them better.
Marketing Cookies: These are used to show you ads that are relevant to your interests.
Who Uses These Technologies?
Both we and our partners (like advertisers and analytics providers) may use these technologies.
What if I Don't Want Cookies?
You can usually change your browser settings to block cookies, but this might affect how our services work.
For more details about specific technologies we use, please check the links below:
Facebook Audience Network
We may use Facebook Audience Network to show you ads on our platforms. This service uses technologies similar to cookies to learn about your preferences and deliver ads that may be more relevant to you. This information may include identifiers for mobile devices (like Android Advertising ID or Advertising Identifier for iOS).
Facebook Privacy Policy link
Google Analytics
We use cookies to better understand how people use our services. This helps us see things like how many people visit, which pages are popular, and where visitors come from. This information helps us improve our services and make them more useful for you.
Google Privacy Policy
Google Firebase
We use Google Firebase to get a better understanding of how people use our services. This tool gives us insights into things like overall usage and traffic patterns, helping us identify areas where we can make improvements for a better user experience.
Google Privacy Policy
Unity Ads
We may offer you the option to watch video ads from Unity Ads in exchange for in-game rewards. While we don't share your information with Unity Ads, they may collect and store information about your ad interactions. This helps them show you ads that might be more relevant to you.
Unity Privacy Policies
AdMob
We use Google AdMob to show ads in our mobile apps. This helps us earn revenue so we can continue to provide and improve our services. AdMob may collect and use your data to personalize ads and measure their effectiveness.
Google Privacy Policy
Applovin
We may use AppLovin to show you ads on our services. They use cookies to learn about your interests across different websites and apps, so you see ads that are more relevant to you. This information doesn't reveal your identity, but it helps us and our partners understand how well our advertising is working.
Applovin Privacy Policy
AppsFlyer
We use AppsFlyer, a tool that helps us understand how people find and use our services. This helps us see which marketing campaigns are working best and how we can improve our overall performance. AppsFlyer collects information about how you interact with our services, but this information is made anonymous and used only for statistical purposes.
AppsFlyer Privacy Policy
Facebook
We may use Facebook to show you ads for our games while you're playing other games. Facebook uses cookies to learn about your interests across different games and apps, allowing them to show you ads for our games that you might be interested in. While this information doesn't directly reveal your personal identity, it helps Facebook recognize you across different games to tailor ads effectively.
Facebook Privacy Policy
Ironsource
We partner with IronSource mediation to show ads in our apps. This helps us earn revenue so we can keep providing you with great games and services. IronSource may collect and use your data to personalize ads and measure their effectiveness.
Ironsource Privacy Policy
Mintegral
Mintegral uses cookies to personalize ads displayed in our service.
Mintegral Privacy Policy
Tapjoy
We use Tapjoy to bot show offers in our apps and to promote our games in third party apps. Tapjoy may collect and use your data to personalize ads.
Tapjoy Privacy Policy
Data Erasure
Data we collect are crucial for the game functionality and basic measurement. You have right to request deletion of your game account so the data we collect will be deleted. If you wish to do so, please,
send us an email to UserDataDeletion@w.aldagames.com with information about your account
. In case of our older games, data about your account are not stored anywhere on our servers so you can only delete your saved data in the game itself.
Games supporting account deletion:
World War Polygon
Transport Tycoon Empire: City
Polygon Fantasy
Summoners Raid
Zombero
